OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782227911
OL,3,CRail provider announces reduced
OL,4,Ctimetables amid record breaking
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FSouth Western Railway (SWR) has
OL,8,Fannounced fewer services will run
OL,9,Facross its network until Thursday amid
OL,10,Fsweltering temperatures for much of
OL,11,Fsouthern England.
OL,13,FThe rail provider said an amended
OL,14,Ftimetable will be in place from
OL,15,FTuesday to Thursday.
OL,17,FPassengers are being advised to only
OL,18,Ftravel if it's necessary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
