FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782227911
OL,3,CRail provider announces reduced
OL,4,Ctimetables amid record breaking
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FIt comes after the Met Office issued a
OL,8,Frare red weather warning for extreme
OL,9,Fheat, which comes into force on
OL,10,FWednesday and covers much of the SWR
OL,11,Fnetwork.
OL,13,FPotentially record breaking
OL,14,Ftemperatures - which could soar up to
OL,15,F40C - have been forecast in some parts
OL,16,Fof England and Wales.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782227911
OL,3,CRail provider announces reduced
OL,4,Ctimetables amid record breaking
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FSWR said it will reveal details of its
OL,8,Famended timetables for Wednesday and
OL,9,FThursday at 2am on Wednesday morning.
OL,11,FTuesday's timetable has already been
OL,12,Freleased.
OL,14,FThe rail provider has warned
OL,15,Fpassengers to expect busier services
OL,16,Fand longer journey times as its trains
OL,17,Fwill be travelling at reduced speeds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
