OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782227911
OL,3,CRail provider announces reduced
OL,4,Ctimetables amid record breaking
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FServices could still be delayed or
OL,8,Fcanceled, and anyone travelling should
OL,9,Fbring plenty of hydration with them,
OL,10,FSWR said.
OL,12,FStuart Meek, Chief Operating Officer
OL,13,Fof SWR and Network Rail Wessex
OL,14,Fapologised for the disruption caused
OL,15,Fto passengers and offered his thanks
OL,16,Fas staff "respond to these record-
OL,17,Fbreaking conditions".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
